WEBVTT

01:43.050 --> 01:46.020
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.140 --> 01:49.090
[Episode 30]

01:49.140 --> 01:49.990
Help!

01:49.990 --> 01:51.560
-Mr. Wen! Mr. Wen!
-Help!

01:51.560 --> 01:52.630
Get off me!

01:52.710 --> 01:53.470
Help!

01:53.550 --> 01:55.039
This is my son!

01:55.360 --> 01:56.979
I'm his father!

03:14.850 --> 03:17.640
[Outpatient]

03:49.270 --> 03:50.320
You got into another fight?

03:53.020 --> 03:53.910
What happened?

03:56.910 --> 03:57.690
My dad…

03:58.670 --> 03:59.630
found my house.

04:01.350 --> 04:02.390
Your dad hit you?

04:03.040 --> 04:05.260
Because I saw He Yan.

04:06.470 --> 04:07.900
He lost it again.

04:08.510 --> 04:09.790
You're an adult now.

04:10.510 --> 04:12.030
Why does your dad still treat you like this?

04:13.990 --> 04:14.600
I don't know

04:14.630 --> 04:15.870
how he even found my house.

04:20.160 --> 04:20.860
Lu Yan,

04:21.630 --> 04:22.760
I'm sorry.

04:23.160 --> 04:24.560
That night at dinner, I…

04:25.630 --> 04:26.470
I lost control.

04:29.830 --> 04:31.230
You don't need to apologize to me.

04:32.110 --> 04:33.390
You didn't do anything wrong to me.

04:36.470 --> 04:37.760
So you also think

04:38.420 --> 04:39.260
I was wrong?

04:40.159 --> 04:41.630
I won't judge

04:42.950 --> 04:43.980
whether you were right or wrong.

04:46.210 --> 04:48.220
But after you left that night,

04:48.880 --> 04:50.870
Auntie was so sad she fainted.

04:53.250 --> 04:54.130
Wen Peng,

04:56.790 --> 04:57.680
that matter happened

04:57.710 --> 04:58.909
so many years ago.

04:59.860 --> 05:01.900
You guys need to have a proper conversation.

05:03.090 --> 05:04.630
If you can accept it, good.

05:04.650 --> 05:05.520
If you can't,

05:07.150 --> 05:08.240
just let it go.

05:09.520 --> 05:10.560
What if I can't let it go?

05:12.630 --> 05:13.790
Then I'm afraid you won't get another chance.

05:16.480 --> 05:17.300
Chance?

05:20.230 --> 05:21.680
The day I was abandoned,

05:21.780 --> 05:22.520
I already knew

05:22.550 --> 05:23.790
there were no more chances in my life.

05:27.710 --> 05:28.800
Do you know how many times

05:28.830 --> 05:29.670
I've thought about killing myself?

05:30.910 --> 05:31.790
About dying?

05:33.080 --> 05:35.060
I thought about taking my dad with me.

05:36.810 --> 05:37.650
When my mom found out

05:37.690 --> 05:38.370
I was dead,

05:38.430 --> 05:40.710
she'd be heartbroken.

05:41.630 --> 05:43.200
And in that moment, I'd feel like

05:44.040 --> 05:45.320
someone still cared about me.

05:47.950 --> 05:48.980
There was a time

05:49.070 --> 05:50.300
when I really wanted to die,

05:50.350 --> 05:51.310
but someone saved me.

05:54.750 --> 05:55.470
Who?

05:56.909 --> 05:57.470
You.

06:02.540 --> 06:03.370
[Dangerous Water Depth, No Swimming]

06:02.700 --> 06:04.060
W-What are you doing?

06:06.720 --> 06:07.390
Wen?

06:08.980 --> 06:10.470
The sign says,

06:10.470 --> 06:12.190
"Dangerous Water Depth."

06:21.150 --> 06:22.270
I know you might have forgotten,

06:22.270 --> 06:23.070
but…

06:24.870 --> 06:26.590
After my mom

06:26.610 --> 06:27.570
left me,

06:27.600 --> 06:28.920
that was the only time

06:29.230 --> 06:30.380
that I didn't feel alone.

06:31.470 --> 06:32.840
You reached out to me,

06:32.950 --> 06:33.670
and for once…

06:36.470 --> 06:37.909
the world felt calm.

06:42.240 --> 06:42.990
Lu Yan,

06:44.659 --> 06:46.240
can you save me one more time?

06:52.030 --> 06:54.050
I know you love

06:54.760 --> 06:55.700
Jiang Chengyi,

06:56.409 --> 06:57.659
but he already has a family,

06:57.680 --> 06:59.050
parents,

06:59.110 --> 07:00.280
and plenty of friends.

07:00.390 --> 07:01.280
I have nothing.

07:01.310 --> 07:02.310
All I have left is you!

07:05.660 --> 07:06.830
You're drunk.

07:08.020 --> 07:08.680
You don't even know

07:08.720 --> 07:09.590
what you're saying.

07:10.490 --> 07:11.790
I'm perfectly sober now,

07:11.870 --> 07:12.810
but I'm in so much pain.

07:13.150 --> 07:14.650
I don't want to keep going home

07:14.710 --> 07:15.710
to an empty,

07:15.830 --> 07:17.150
lifeless house.

07:19.820 --> 07:21.210
Just pity me

07:21.960 --> 07:23.040
and stay with me,

07:23.070 --> 07:23.750
okay?

07:27.990 --> 07:28.780
How about this?

07:31.630 --> 07:33.130
Just tell me what you want,

07:33.690 --> 07:35.040
and I'll give it to you.

07:35.710 --> 07:36.380
Okay?

07:38.750 --> 07:39.430
Okay.

07:43.220 --> 07:44.960
Let me ask you a question.

07:45.780 --> 07:46.430
Go ahead.

07:51.710 --> 07:52.390
Deng Man,

07:54.500 --> 07:55.480
Wang Qianqian,

07:57.980 --> 07:58.750
and Ding Jing,

08:01.220 --> 08:02.490
did their deaths

08:04.140 --> 08:05.490
have anything to do with you?

08:29.380 --> 08:30.640
If I tell you,

08:30.680 --> 08:31.710
will you be with me?

08:33.500 --> 08:35.260
This isn't a trade.

08:35.980 --> 08:37.210
I'm asking you a question.

08:37.299 --> 08:38.070
No, no, no.

08:38.070 --> 08:40.390
I'm not asking for much.

08:42.240 --> 08:42.919
Seven days.

08:45.100 --> 08:45.670
Three days.

08:45.690 --> 08:46.840
Even one day.

08:48.670 --> 08:49.350
One hour.

08:50.280 --> 08:51.250
One minute.

08:54.730 --> 08:55.540
Don't touch me.

08:55.850 --> 08:56.810
Why can't you even spare me

08:56.830 --> 08:57.510
one minute?

08:58.020 --> 08:59.000
All these years,

08:59.030 --> 08:59.750
I've always been there for you.

08:59.920 --> 09:00.550
Haven't you ever felt

09:00.570 --> 09:01.810
anything for me?

09:02.000 --> 09:02.510
Listen to me.

09:02.530 --> 09:03.330
What do you want?

09:03.360 --> 09:04.010
Listen to me!

09:08.870 --> 09:09.720
Sorry.

09:09.750 --> 09:10.670
The number you have dialed

09:10.710 --> 09:12.230
is not being answered at the moment.

09:12.330 --> 09:13.580
Please redial later.

09:13.950 --> 09:14.820
Sorry...

09:14.850 --> 09:16.610
How am I any worse than Jiang Chengyi?

09:16.640 --> 09:17.970
Why are you treating me like this?

09:18.030 --> 09:19.240
You're nowhere near his level.

09:19.320 --> 09:19.980
Help!

09:20.040 --> 09:20.660
Hel…

09:20.680 --> 09:22.340
Don't shout, don't shout!

09:22.390 --> 09:23.070
Don't shout.

09:23.090 --> 09:23.690
Please, don't shout.

09:23.750 --> 09:24.600
Think about it.

09:24.870 --> 09:25.440
All this time,

09:25.470 --> 09:26.280
have I ever hurt you?

09:26.300 --> 09:26.950
Have I ever

09:26.990 --> 09:27.830
done anything to hurt you

09:27.870 --> 09:28.640
to make you treat me like this?

09:28.750 --> 09:29.350
I love you.

09:29.430 --> 09:30.160
I really love you.

09:30.190 --> 09:30.750
I truly love you.

09:30.780 --> 09:31.830
Help! Help!

09:31.830 --> 09:33.250
I love you! I swear, I love you!

09:33.890 --> 09:34.710
I love you.

09:35.820 --> 09:36.910
Help!

09:41.020 --> 09:42.060
What are you doing?

09:45.040 --> 09:45.890
How are you?

09:46.250 --> 09:47.140
Are you okay?

09:49.740 --> 09:50.790
Where are you hurt?

09:51.650 --> 09:53.000
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

09:55.620 --> 09:56.520
Captain Jiang,

09:58.030 --> 09:59.450
you can't catch the criminal,

09:59.780 --> 10:01.280
but you sure visit the hospital a lot.

10:01.480 --> 10:02.660
I don't want to waste time with you.

10:02.710 --> 10:03.600
Get lost.

10:08.340 --> 10:09.130
It's okay now.

10:11.950 --> 10:12.750
Lu Yan,

10:15.840 --> 10:17.010
are you coming with me?

10:23.950 --> 10:26.220
Either you walk out on your own,

10:26.980 --> 10:28.600
or I'll take you to the police station myself.

10:28.760 --> 10:29.830
Pick one.

10:51.820 --> 10:52.510
It's okay.

10:53.500 --> 10:54.450
It's okay now.

10:54.470 --> 10:55.900
Don't be scared.

10:57.830 --> 10:58.550
It's okay now.

11:00.470 --> 11:01.590
You must be terrified.

11:03.370 --> 11:04.610
I'm here. I'm here.

12:36.590 --> 12:37.560
Is this the place?

12:38.430 --> 12:39.370
Yeah, somewhere around here.

12:39.400 --> 12:40.600
I've asked around.

12:40.710 --> 12:41.570
People say Ma Cheng

12:41.610 --> 12:42.450
almost plays mahjong

12:42.480 --> 12:43.470
in this neighborhood every day.

12:45.350 --> 12:46.790
Alright, let's look for him.

12:49.550 --> 12:52.930
[Mutao Mahjong]

12:49.790 --> 12:50.480
Two Crack.

12:51.050 --> 12:52.260
How's my hand looking?

12:52.290 --> 12:53.490
Not bad. It's good.

12:53.720 --> 12:55.310
Not bad.

12:56.120 --> 12:57.060
Which one of you is playing?

12:57.150 --> 12:58.380
Which one of you is playing?

12:59.470 --> 13:00.110
One Dot.

13:01.070 --> 13:01.600
Six Bamboo.

13:01.670 --> 13:02.810
That's a good move.

13:02.950 --> 13:03.720
Six Bamboo.

13:04.850 --> 13:06.240
Hurry up, hurry up.

13:06.240 --> 13:06.830
Hurry up.

13:06.880 --> 13:08.130
I'm about to win.

13:08.430 --> 13:09.740
I'm about to win here!

13:10.190 --> 13:11.230
One Circle again.

13:12.210 --> 13:13.270
Playing with you old-timers…

13:13.270 --> 13:13.920
West Wind.

13:13.950 --> 13:14.440
is such a hassle.

13:15.780 --> 13:16.700
Which one of you is playing?

13:18.590 --> 13:20.000
Ma Cheng, you're on a roll today.

13:20.030 --> 13:21.000
When am I not…

13:22.040 --> 13:23.040
Who are you?

13:27.170 --> 13:28.140
[Public Security]

13:29.540 --> 13:30.270
Are you playing or not?

13:30.290 --> 13:31.010
Just play.

13:31.040 --> 13:32.710
An old friend of mine is here.

13:32.750 --> 13:34.680
I'll be back in a minute.

13:35.390 --> 13:36.150
Play for me.

13:36.230 --> 13:36.830
Alright.

13:36.830 --> 13:38.030
Easy. We just need to ask you something.

13:38.110 --> 13:39.110
Alright.

13:38.940 --> 13:40.710
[Mutao Mahjong]

13:39.240 --> 13:41.070
Come on, quick.

13:41.290 --> 13:41.820
Yes,

13:42.170 --> 13:43.620
I was Yan Mei's caregiver.

13:44.820 --> 13:45.840
About two years ago,

13:45.870 --> 13:46.970
I looked after her.

13:47.510 --> 13:48.950
Who hired you at the time?

13:48.970 --> 13:49.680
Do you still remember?

13:49.790 --> 13:50.830
It was a man

13:51.190 --> 13:53.000
in his thirties.

13:53.350 --> 13:54.760
We only met once.

13:55.690 --> 13:57.320
After handling the hospital admission,

13:57.340 --> 13:58.370
I never saw him again.

13:59.150 --> 14:00.390
How did you stay in contact?

14:00.470 --> 14:01.320
By phone.

14:01.720 --> 14:02.750
I remember

14:02.790 --> 14:04.500
we'd usually talk once a week.

14:04.690 --> 14:05.960
He also gave me a card

14:06.040 --> 14:07.220
to cover

14:07.510 --> 14:08.580
all the expenses.

14:11.710 --> 14:13.230
Later, Yan Mei was discharged,

14:13.390 --> 14:13.950
right?

14:14.590 --> 14:15.350
At the time,

14:15.390 --> 14:16.670
Yan Mei's condition was quite serious.

14:17.120 --> 14:18.240
So I notified him right away.

14:18.920 --> 14:20.070
After he found out,

14:21.100 --> 14:22.470
he told me to arrange for her discharge

14:22.750 --> 14:23.790
and take her home.

14:24.180 --> 14:25.710
Actually, it's understandable.

14:25.770 --> 14:27.420
At that stage,

14:27.440 --> 14:28.140
treatment or no treatment

14:28.170 --> 14:29.310
didn't make much of a difference.

14:29.430 --> 14:31.110
So I sent Yan Mei home.

14:31.150 --> 14:32.750
When I contacted him again,

14:32.890 --> 14:34.620
he said I could leave

14:34.650 --> 14:35.800
and he'd be there soon.

14:36.550 --> 14:37.870
I thought about

14:38.500 --> 14:39.720
meeting him before I left,

14:40.070 --> 14:41.710
just in case something happened

14:41.730 --> 14:42.920
to the patient

14:42.950 --> 14:43.790
and I wouldn't be able to explain it.

14:44.810 --> 14:46.760
But he told me

14:46.950 --> 14:47.860
once she was home,

14:47.990 --> 14:49.150
my job was done,

14:49.570 --> 14:50.780
and I could go.

14:51.510 --> 14:52.600
So after that,

14:52.630 --> 14:53.390
I left.

14:59.420 --> 15:00.450
Take a look.

15:00.710 --> 15:01.470
Is this the man?

15:05.350 --> 15:05.910
No.

15:06.390 --> 15:07.040
Are you sure?

15:07.150 --> 15:07.750
I'm sure.

15:09.650 --> 15:10.770
Can you describe him to us?

15:10.870 --> 15:12.210
What did he look like,

15:12.710 --> 15:13.990
or did he have any distinctive features?

15:14.270 --> 15:15.080
We mostly stayed in touch

15:15.110 --> 15:15.910
over the phone,

15:16.700 --> 15:18.690
but from his voice,

15:18.910 --> 15:19.970
I'd say he was probably local.

15:20.150 --> 15:21.240
Do you still have his number?

15:21.280 --> 15:22.330
I deleted it a long time ago.

15:26.690 --> 15:28.430
Do you remember Yan Mei's address?

16:18.680 --> 16:19.430
That day,

16:19.500 --> 16:21.230
I sent Yan Mei here,

16:21.330 --> 16:22.820
made the call, and left.

16:50.540 --> 16:51.700
Officers,

16:52.410 --> 16:53.690
is there anything else?

16:53.730 --> 16:54.620
No, nothing else.

16:54.640 --> 16:56.060
You can go. Thank you.

16:56.080 --> 16:57.080
If we need anything, I'll get in touch.

16:58.280 --> 16:58.790
I'm leaving.

16:59.210 --> 17:00.100
Ma Cheng.

17:01.270 --> 17:02.390
Do you smoke?

17:02.410 --> 17:03.630
I don't.

17:03.650 --> 17:04.280
Why?

17:06.319 --> 17:08.170
Nothing. You can go.

17:08.390 --> 17:09.030
Okay.

17:09.260 --> 17:10.000
I'm off.

17:12.030 --> 17:12.630
Professor Yu.

17:17.420 --> 17:18.400
Look.

17:19.640 --> 17:20.680
These medicines

17:20.700 --> 17:23.050
should be the ones Yan Mei was taking.

17:30.870 --> 17:31.650
And this.

17:32.070 --> 17:33.130
Aside from you, Ma Cheng,

17:33.310 --> 17:34.770
and me,

17:35.230 --> 17:36.270
someone else has been here.

17:41.560 --> 17:43.150
So, you think

17:43.420 --> 17:45.280
Yan Mei is already deceased, right?

17:46.470 --> 17:47.530
Yes, Captain Jiang.

17:47.690 --> 17:48.850
Based on Ma Cheng's account,

17:48.920 --> 17:50.690
Yan Mei's condition was very severe at the time.

17:51.070 --> 17:52.320
Taking her away in that state…

17:52.370 --> 17:54.030
It would've been either to save her

17:54.430 --> 17:55.790
or to kill her.

17:55.870 --> 17:56.510
Exactly.

17:57.330 --> 17:59.120
And so far,

17:59.150 --> 18:00.270
we haven't found

18:00.270 --> 18:02.070
any information or clues

18:02.070 --> 18:03.550
about the person who hired Ma Cheng.

18:04.510 --> 18:05.600
I suspect

18:05.870 --> 18:07.970
this person meant

18:08.070 --> 18:09.270
to hide their identity.

18:10.320 --> 18:11.120
Here's the plan.

18:11.230 --> 18:12.950
You'll stay a couple more days,

18:14.100 --> 18:15.330
visit a few more departments,

18:15.470 --> 18:17.190
and see if you can find any leads.

18:18.070 --> 18:18.710
Alright.

18:19.120 --> 18:19.840
If anything comes up,

18:19.870 --> 18:20.710
I'll tell you immediately.

18:21.390 --> 18:22.790
Okay. Thanks.

18:26.380 --> 18:27.590
Alright, Professor Yu,

18:27.620 --> 18:28.530
I'm heading back to rest.

18:29.750 --> 18:30.390
Liu Hao.

18:31.630 --> 18:32.750
Go buy several packs of cigarettes.

18:33.700 --> 18:35.100
In the next couple of days,

18:35.270 --> 18:36.240
if we encounter any suspicious people,

18:36.270 --> 18:37.410
you'll offer them a cigarette.

18:37.680 --> 18:39.190
After all, there aren't many

18:39.210 --> 18:41.100
who bite their cigarette butts like this.

18:42.600 --> 18:43.270
Got it.

18:56.250 --> 18:57.050
Hello, Qin Yue?

18:57.900 --> 19:00.740
Well, check Yan Mei's

19:00.880 --> 19:01.900
medical records for me.

19:03.050 --> 19:03.690
Yes.

19:05.480 --> 19:06.320
Let me know once you've found anything.

19:17.430 --> 19:18.070
What's up?

19:18.910 --> 19:20.120
Nothing, just work.

19:20.910 --> 19:21.950
I made something tasty.

19:21.990 --> 19:22.830
Want to try it?

19:23.510 --> 19:24.990
Sure. Let me see what you made.

19:25.310 --> 19:25.840
Come on.

19:26.300 --> 19:27.050
Go take a look.

19:29.010 --> 19:31.780
[Police]

19:46.150 --> 19:47.360
What's this about?

19:47.680 --> 19:49.220
You got me here

19:49.620 --> 19:50.770
but won't say anything.

19:56.540 --> 19:58.280
I've already explained everything.

19:59.210 --> 20:01.130
Do what you want with me.

20:02.210 --> 20:03.290
I'll accept it.

20:12.850 --> 20:13.780
Come in.

20:14.620 --> 20:15.380
Captain Jiang.

20:15.900 --> 20:16.500
Thank you.

20:23.950 --> 20:27.030
Chengzhou Second People's Hospital,

20:28.440 --> 20:29.440
Yan Mei,

20:29.990 --> 20:30.510
female,

20:30.830 --> 20:31.510
51 years old,

20:32.470 --> 20:33.330
from Chengzhou,

20:33.570 --> 20:34.290
Han ethnicity,

20:34.630 --> 20:36.600
diagnosed with uremia, right?

20:37.630 --> 20:38.710
We looked into it.

20:39.470 --> 20:40.350
Your mother

20:40.640 --> 20:41.750
stayed

20:41.750 --> 20:43.390
in the Second People's Hospital

20:43.390 --> 20:44.090
in 2021 for uremia

20:44.120 --> 20:45.390
for six months.

20:45.410 --> 20:46.400
After she was discharged,

20:46.950 --> 20:47.720
she didn't receive treatment

20:47.750 --> 20:48.670
at any other hospital.

20:50.120 --> 20:51.360
I thought she'd been sent abroad,

20:52.310 --> 20:54.050
but I checked her travel records—

20:54.190 --> 20:54.830
she wasn't.

20:55.400 --> 20:56.710
She wasn't treated abroad,

20:56.730 --> 20:58.150
nor was she treated domestically.

20:58.170 --> 21:00.040
But uremia is a condition

21:00.790 --> 21:02.130
that requires treatment.

21:02.350 --> 21:03.270
Without it, she wouldn't survive for long.

21:05.870 --> 21:06.920
So after I think about it,

21:08.350 --> 21:09.470
there's only one possibility left.

21:09.490 --> 21:10.370
Impossible.

21:12.160 --> 21:13.280
He showed me

21:13.310 --> 21:14.230
photos of her.

21:17.100 --> 21:18.330
He seems a nice guy.

21:18.780 --> 21:19.530
He…

21:20.090 --> 21:21.490
helped you take care of your mom, right?

21:32.310 --> 21:33.470
Don't try to trick me.

21:35.080 --> 21:36.440
I won't say anything.

21:42.810 --> 21:44.370
I know you won't say anything.

21:44.590 --> 21:45.830
But I have to tell you,

21:46.240 --> 21:47.360
everything

21:48.070 --> 21:49.380
I've said to you here

21:49.630 --> 21:50.870
is backed by evidence.

21:51.290 --> 21:52.130
I won't lie to you,

21:52.160 --> 21:53.610
and I have no reason to.

21:57.390 --> 21:58.500
I just want to check

21:58.950 --> 22:00.400
if my investigation is headed

22:00.430 --> 22:01.170
in the right direction.

22:01.350 --> 22:02.830
Since it is, I hope you know

22:03.760 --> 22:04.950
I also wish

22:07.150 --> 22:08.510
it didn't turn out like this.

22:11.990 --> 22:13.060
I don't want to see

22:13.540 --> 22:15.080
all your hard work

22:15.100 --> 22:16.020
end up

22:16.070 --> 22:17.390
with a result like this.

22:36.170 --> 22:40.680
[Forge safety through actions; define responsibility through dedication.]

22:37.890 --> 22:38.870
Jiang,

22:38.890 --> 22:40.090
I learned a lot from you today.

22:40.110 --> 22:41.120
That was impressive.

22:40.680 --> 22:43.470
[Legal Affairs Office]

22:41.140 --> 22:42.040
You're so experienced.

22:42.090 --> 22:43.150
Don't mention it.

22:43.180 --> 22:44.340
I don't want to deal with people like that anymore.

22:46.510 --> 22:47.980
How are things with the film crew?

22:48.020 --> 22:48.880
Just as you expected,

22:48.910 --> 22:50.020
no leads.

22:50.170 --> 22:51.590
Ever since my last confrontation

22:51.610 --> 22:52.660
with Wen Peng,

22:52.680 --> 22:54.240
the entire crew has been avoiding me.

22:54.670 --> 22:55.480
But I'm sure of one thing:

22:55.510 --> 22:57.190
Wen Peng is definitely hiding something.

22:57.930 --> 22:59.110
Them avoiding you isn't a bad thing.

22:59.240 --> 23:00.730
If he's started avoiding you,

23:00.790 --> 23:03.030
it means he's close to slipping up.

23:03.280 --> 23:04.020
Keep watching him.

23:04.350 --> 23:05.030
No rush.

23:07.890 --> 23:08.720
Where is everyone?

23:08.790 --> 23:09.960
They've all been sent out.

23:13.470 --> 23:13.950
Zhong,

23:14.660 --> 23:15.840
do you think this plan will work?

23:15.960 --> 23:17.190
Definitely.

23:17.320 --> 23:18.750
For a habitual scammer like him,

23:19.390 --> 23:20.730
he won't be able to resist

23:20.760 --> 23:21.760
the temptation of easy money.

23:27.560 --> 23:28.600
Dalu, here he is.

23:29.620 --> 23:34.310
[Mr. Ke]

23:32.250 --> 23:34.070
Hello? Have you arrived?

23:34.350 --> 23:35.640
Almost there, Mr. Ke.

23:35.660 --> 23:37.310
We just got off the bus,

23:37.330 --> 23:38.450
just a few hundred meters away.

23:38.710 --> 23:39.270
Alright.

23:39.520 --> 23:40.670
We'll meet downstairs

23:40.700 --> 23:42.410
at my company, okay?

23:42.500 --> 23:43.770
Got it, Mr. Ke.

23:43.970 --> 23:45.210
Oh, Mr. Ke,

23:45.420 --> 23:47.530
I just want to confirm.

23:47.610 --> 23:48.960
If we pay

23:48.990 --> 23:50.240
this sponsorship fee,

23:50.270 --> 23:51.480
we'll definitely get into

23:51.480 --> 23:52.980
Wanglou Corporation, right?

23:53.010 --> 23:53.910
Of course.

23:54.010 --> 23:55.730
I told you.

23:55.750 --> 23:57.760
I know the big bosses there very well.

23:57.800 --> 23:59.570
I can get you all in.

23:59.590 --> 24:01.640
Alright, thanks, Mr. Ke.

24:01.670 --> 24:02.500
We're all

24:02.530 --> 24:03.330
counting on you.

24:03.360 --> 24:03.880
No problem.

24:03.910 --> 24:04.670
Hurry up.

24:04.700 --> 24:05.420
Be careful.

24:05.880 --> 24:06.650
See you in a bit.

24:09.150 --> 24:09.990
What a scammer.

24:32.920 --> 24:34.570
Hey, what are you doing?

24:34.610 --> 24:35.730
How dare you do this

24:35.750 --> 24:36.790
in broad daylight?

24:36.880 --> 24:37.640
As a scammer,

24:37.660 --> 24:38.850
you don't get to ask us that!

24:38.990 --> 24:39.790
Scammer?

24:39.830 --> 24:41.030
What scammer?

24:41.060 --> 24:42.230
You've got the wrong guy!

24:42.550 --> 24:44.020
I told you.

24:44.060 --> 24:45.970
[Convert to Text] [Tag]

24:44.150 --> 24:45.950
I know the big bosses there very well.

24:46.030 --> 24:48.000
I can get you all in.

24:48.120 --> 24:50.020
How can you scam college students?

24:50.040 --> 24:51.240
You even said you know

24:51.270 --> 24:51.950
those big bosses well.

24:51.970 --> 24:53.220
You've got no shame, do you?

24:53.250 --> 24:54.620
Are you even human?

24:55.240 --> 24:56.360
Zhong, don't waste your breath.

24:56.390 --> 24:56.870
Let's take him to the police station.

24:56.870 --> 24:58.230
No, no! Guys, please,

24:58.250 --> 24:59.800
cut me some slack.

24:59.820 --> 25:00.870
I haven't

25:00.900 --> 25:01.530
done this in a long time.

25:01.560 --> 25:03.170
I'll give you one last chance.

25:03.330 --> 25:04.910
Tell me the truth.

25:05.260 --> 25:06.360
Are you working with Wen Peng

25:06.390 --> 25:07.430
to scam us?

25:07.670 --> 25:08.470
No, no, no!

25:08.510 --> 25:09.570
I had no choice

25:09.630 --> 25:10.660
but to follow his orders.

25:10.690 --> 25:11.870
He made me do this.

25:12.070 --> 25:13.120
Is this "he" you're talking about

25:13.140 --> 25:14.290
Wen Peng?

25:14.590 --> 25:15.370
Wen Peng, yeah.

25:15.390 --> 25:15.790
He…

25:15.790 --> 25:17.180
he opened a film company

25:17.210 --> 25:18.280
and made me the boss.

25:18.430 --> 25:19.480
I owe him money.

25:19.500 --> 25:20.750
Guys, I owe him money,

25:20.780 --> 25:21.670
so I had no choice

25:21.870 --> 25:23.360
but to follow his orders.

25:23.430 --> 25:25.110
I was just paid to do what he said!

25:25.230 --> 25:25.910
Dalu,

25:26.070 --> 25:27.120
take him to the police station.

25:27.300 --> 25:28.550
Wait. Why are you still doing that?

25:28.550 --> 25:29.350
I've told you the truth!

25:29.350 --> 25:30.350
Move. Shut up.

25:30.640 --> 25:31.420
Wen Peng!

25:32.070 --> 25:32.640
Mr. Zhong.

25:32.710 --> 25:33.780
Get lost!

25:34.290 --> 25:34.840
Zhong…

25:35.690 --> 25:36.810
Why?

25:37.120 --> 25:39.070
Zhong, calm down.

25:44.630 --> 25:45.560
What do you mean?

25:45.680 --> 25:47.400
Why did you set me up?

25:48.560 --> 25:49.360
Set you up?

25:49.710 --> 25:51.000
The IP is fake.

25:51.030 --> 25:52.310
Mr. Ke is fake.

25:52.350 --> 25:53.770
All those so-called investors

25:53.800 --> 25:55.280
of yours are fake!

25:56.690 --> 25:57.880
I honestly don't understand

25:57.910 --> 25:58.550
what you're talking about.

25:58.890 --> 26:00.070
Mr. Ke does own

26:00.110 --> 26:00.790
a film company,

26:00.810 --> 26:02.630
and I've contacted the investors.

26:03.030 --> 26:04.680
Our collaboration is real.

26:04.890 --> 26:05.750
I don't understand

26:05.790 --> 26:06.710
why you're saying that.

26:06.920 --> 26:07.730
Cut it out.

26:08.680 --> 26:09.550
That Mr. Ke

26:09.590 --> 26:11.040
has already admitted it.

26:11.070 --> 26:12.280
You set up the company for him

26:12.350 --> 26:14.040
and helped him with the scam!

26:14.360 --> 26:15.470
Do you have proof?

26:27.340 --> 26:28.110
Zhong.

26:28.660 --> 26:29.960
I suggest you study the law

26:29.990 --> 26:31.390
in your free time.

26:32.120 --> 26:33.230
Just because

26:33.410 --> 26:34.200
Mr. Ke said

26:34.230 --> 26:35.310
I told him to do it

26:35.630 --> 26:37.040
doesn't prove that

26:37.070 --> 26:38.510
our collaboration

26:38.530 --> 26:39.850
is illegal.

26:42.510 --> 26:43.800
I don't get it.

26:44.180 --> 26:45.840
You can only get a few million yuan from me.

26:45.940 --> 26:47.400
Do you really need that money?

26:47.540 --> 26:48.620
Your money

26:48.670 --> 26:50.150
doesn't mean much to me.

26:50.280 --> 26:52.190
But making you lose money

26:52.190 --> 26:53.790
means a lot to me.

26:56.830 --> 26:57.870
What's that supposed to mean?

27:01.350 --> 27:02.440
It means I just want to make you

27:02.470 --> 27:03.710
a downright loser.

27:05.100 --> 27:06.110
Only then does my scheme

27:06.110 --> 27:06.950
feel worthwhile.

27:09.630 --> 27:11.440
What did I ever do to you

27:11.470 --> 27:12.930
to deserve this?

27:13.720 --> 27:15.230
Since we met,

27:15.540 --> 27:17.070
how many times have you meddled in others' affairs?

27:18.230 --> 27:19.510
Meddled?

27:23.130 --> 27:25.650
Are you talking about Jiang and Lu Yan?

27:27.000 --> 27:28.640
Not bad, Zhong.

27:29.080 --> 27:30.550
You've finally caught on.

27:31.980 --> 27:33.180
I really don't get it.

27:33.180 --> 27:34.350
Why did you have to stick your nose

27:34.610 --> 27:36.140
into their business?

27:40.060 --> 27:41.480
So just because of that,

27:41.510 --> 27:42.990
you want to take revenge on me?

27:43.060 --> 27:43.630
Yes.

27:43.670 --> 27:45.520
I just want to see you look like a beaten dog

27:45.540 --> 27:46.760
and become a pathetic loser.

27:46.780 --> 27:47.910
Because in my eyes,

27:47.940 --> 27:50.250
you're nothing more than Jiang Chengyi's dog!

27:50.310 --> 27:51.110
You…

28:00.470 --> 28:01.110
What?

28:02.170 --> 28:03.220
Not going to hit me?

28:12.800 --> 28:14.560
You're going to be a father soon.

28:16.280 --> 28:18.870
Zhong, you need to have a sense of responsibility now!

28:22.710 --> 28:23.390
Calm down.

28:24.830 --> 28:25.740
Calm down.

28:30.390 --> 28:32.190
Calm down.

28:41.320 --> 28:42.150
Zhong.

28:43.250 --> 28:44.720
I've already been merciful.

28:45.440 --> 28:47.290
I've cut you some slack.

28:50.990 --> 28:52.330
If it were someone else,

28:52.350 --> 28:54.280
it wouldn't stop at just losing money.

30:24.070 --> 30:25.260
Come out now.

30:25.490 --> 30:26.480
There's someone at my door.

30:34.270 --> 30:35.100
Professor Yu,

30:35.660 --> 30:36.470
there's no one else in the hallway,

30:36.510 --> 30:37.390
just two staff.

30:52.230 --> 30:53.140
What happened?

30:54.320 --> 30:55.160
Someone was outside my door.

31:00.050 --> 31:00.710
Around

31:00.750 --> 31:01.950
12 o'clock at noon.

31:05.930 --> 31:06.920
This is the second-floor hallway.

31:07.610 --> 31:11.540
[Hallway]

31:13.820 --> 31:20.750
[Hallway]

31:22.340 --> 31:23.260
There really was someone.

31:24.470 --> 31:28.580
[Hallway]

31:31.650 --> 31:32.930
He probably went to the wrong room.

31:32.950 --> 31:33.470
Don't worry.

31:33.490 --> 31:34.660
Our hotel has excellent security.

31:34.680 --> 31:35.370
Just make sure your door…

31:35.390 --> 31:36.580
Can we check the lobby surveillance footage?

31:36.840 --> 31:37.760
Of course.

31:38.090 --> 31:38.810
The lobby.

31:42.080 --> 31:45.430
[Lobby]

31:43.330 --> 31:44.230
Did you

31:44.230 --> 31:44.950
lose something?

31:47.820 --> 31:48.550
Stop there.

31:48.610 --> 31:50.720
[Lobby]

31:54.150 --> 31:56.360
[Lobby]

31:57.690 --> 31:58.820
Yu Bofeng?

31:59.120 --> 31:59.960
It should be him.

32:08.710 --> 32:10.590
So right after Yu Bofeng got out of prison,

32:10.620 --> 32:11.910
he came to Chengzhou to follow us?

32:13.670 --> 32:15.030
Do you think he's trying to get revenge on you?

32:18.990 --> 32:19.710
I don't think so.

32:21.410 --> 32:22.240
I believe he wouldn't

32:22.260 --> 32:23.230
do something like that.

32:26.080 --> 32:26.860
Professor Yu,

32:27.320 --> 32:28.790
Yu Bofeng was a big star

32:28.840 --> 32:29.550
before ending up like this.

32:29.880 --> 32:31.680
It's natural for his mindset to change.

32:32.490 --> 32:34.000
And he does hold resentment

32:34.030 --> 32:34.710
toward both you and Captain Jiang.

32:35.270 --> 32:36.980
We should be cautious.

32:37.590 --> 32:38.750
We can observe

32:38.750 --> 32:39.900
Yu Bofeng a bit longer

32:40.190 --> 32:41.910
to see what his real intentions are.

32:43.130 --> 32:44.470
But honestly,

32:46.180 --> 32:46.830
I don't think

32:46.830 --> 32:48.480
he'll do anything extreme.

32:48.850 --> 32:51.070
The top priority now

32:51.990 --> 32:53.070
is to find Li Ruonan's address.

32:55.900 --> 32:57.480
I'm really sorry.

32:57.670 --> 32:59.020
Manager Sun isn't in today,

32:59.040 --> 33:00.530
but he specifically asked me

33:00.630 --> 33:01.870
to assist you.

33:02.150 --> 33:03.490
Let me introduce myself.

33:03.830 --> 33:04.900
My surname is Wang.

33:05.030 --> 33:06.540
I'm a temp worker here.

33:06.580 --> 33:08.010
You can just call me Wang.

33:08.090 --> 33:08.690
Alright.

33:12.840 --> 33:14.880
What are the specifics of the body

33:14.900 --> 33:16.280
you're looking for?

33:16.750 --> 33:17.630
Female,

33:17.730 --> 33:18.970
around 50 years old.

33:18.990 --> 33:20.690
She should have been sick before she died,

33:20.710 --> 33:22.870
so she was very thin and light.

33:23.010 --> 33:25.010
She died about two years ago.

33:33.010 --> 33:34.350
Among the unclaimed bodies

33:34.390 --> 33:35.850
in the hospital, it seems

33:35.880 --> 33:37.560
none of them matches your description.

33:39.030 --> 33:40.400
But the police station

33:40.470 --> 33:41.320
has a body of a woman

33:41.350 --> 33:42.450
in her 50s.

33:42.550 --> 33:43.230
Maybe that's the one

33:43.310 --> 33:43.950
you're looking for.

33:44.530 --> 33:45.310
Can we take a look

33:45.350 --> 33:46.100
at her basic information?

33:46.300 --> 33:46.950
Sure.

33:50.870 --> 33:53.190
The reason this body

33:53.190 --> 33:54.630
hasn't been claimed

33:54.630 --> 33:56.200
is because all her family members have died.

33:56.440 --> 33:58.760
But her time of death

33:58.780 --> 33:59.860
seems to have been last year.

34:00.230 --> 34:00.860
Here's the name.

34:00.890 --> 34:02.720
See if it matches up.

34:03.130 --> 34:05.270
[Unclaimed Bodies]

34:13.150 --> 34:13.840
By the way,

34:14.960 --> 34:16.900
what kind of case are you working on

34:17.560 --> 34:19.239
that brought you all the way here?

34:20.010 --> 34:20.920
Nothing major.

34:20.960 --> 34:21.800
Thanks for your help.

34:23.810 --> 34:25.139
If I need anything else, I'll get in touch.

34:25.310 --> 34:25.909
Cigarette.

34:30.360 --> 34:31.210
Wang, right?

34:31.270 --> 34:32.120
Here.

34:32.820 --> 34:33.860
Oh, thanks.

34:34.719 --> 34:35.620
I'm afraid

34:35.639 --> 34:36.610
we'll need your help again.

34:36.820 --> 34:37.460
Thank you.

34:38.159 --> 34:38.750
Thank you.

34:42.570 --> 34:43.380
Goodbye.

34:43.600 --> 34:44.350
Thank you.

34:45.250 --> 34:45.909
Goodbye.

35:06.390 --> 35:07.560
Did you notice

35:07.980 --> 35:09.780
the way that guy smoked?

35:10.440 --> 35:11.500
I did.

35:11.950 --> 35:13.260
And he seemed very interested

35:13.310 --> 35:14.230
in what we'd found out.

35:14.530 --> 35:15.410
Exactly.

35:16.970 --> 35:17.840
Find a way to get hold of

35:17.870 --> 35:18.830
one of his cigarette butts.

35:20.500 --> 35:21.110
Got it.
